name: Concorde at the Museum of Flight in Seattle, Washington
description:
Hello everyone, this is a short music video featuring the Concorde at the Museum of Flight at Boeing Field in Seattle, Washington, USA. The one at the museum is G-BOAG, which was the 6th Concorde in British Airways service, and was the 18th Concorde to be built. If you have not visited the Museum of Flight and seen this beautiful bird in person, I highly recommend it, you will not be disappointed. I hope you enjoy the video!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
_____________________________________________________

Music is "Lithium" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
